## 3. Quota Gauge (사용량 표시)

```tsx
import { QuotaGaugeBase } from '@/shared/ui/gauge';

<QuotaGaugeBase
  label={<span className="text-text-muted font-medium">{t('section.quota.label')}</span>}
  used={quota.used}
  total={quota.total}
  warningThreshold={80}
  formatValue={formatStorageSize}
/>
```

색상: 정상 `bg-text-subtle` / 경고 `bg-warning` (>=80%) / 초과 `bg-error` (>=100%)

참고: `src/shared/ui/gauge/QuotaGaugeBase.tsx`

